    <title>Redis学习(1)-常用的五种数据结构</title>
    <link href="/2021/03/26/Redis%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0(1)-%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E7%A7%8D%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84/"/>
    <url>/2021/03/26/Redis%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0(1)-%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E7%A7%8D%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Redis官方文档：<a href="http://www.redis.cn/commands.html#sorted">http://www.redis.cn/commands.html</a></p><h4 id="背景知识一、NoSQL-非关系型数据库-即-Not-Only-SQL"><a href="#背景知识一、NoSQL-非关系型数据库-即-Not-Only-SQL" class="headerlink" title="背景知识一、NoSQL 非关系型数据库 即 Not  Only  SQL"></a>背景知识一、NoSQL 非关系型数据库 即 Not  Only  SQL</h4><h4 id="背景知识二、四类非关系型数据库"><a href="#背景知识二、四类非关系型数据库" class="headerlink" title="背景知识二、四类非关系型数据库"></a>背景知识二、四类非关系型数据库</h4><ol><li>Key-Value:  Redis</li><li>文档型数据库(bson格式):  MongoDB，一个基于分布式存储的数据库</li><li>面向列：HBase  分布式文件系统</li><li>图形化: Neo4J </li></ol><h3 id="1-Redis基础知识"><a href="#1-Redis基础知识" class="headerlink" title="1. Redis基础知识"></a>1. Redis基础知识</h3><p>redis 默认有16个数据库 默认使用的是第0个数据库 可以使用select  index 切换数据库</p><p>Redis-benchmark:  Redis自带性能测试服务</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs bash">SELECT index <span class="hljs-comment">## 选择数据库</span><br>DBSIZE <span class="hljs-comment">## 查看当前数据库大小</span><br>FLUSHALL <span class="hljs-comment">## 清空全部数据库</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-Docker-拉取镜像-创建并启动redis容器"><a href="#2-Docker-拉取镜像-创建并启动redis容器" class="headerlink" title="2. Docker 拉取镜像 创建并启动redis容器"></a>2. Docker 拉取镜像 创建并启动redis容器</h3><figure class="highlight applescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs applescript">docker pull daocloud.io/library/redis:<span class="hljs-number">6.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.3</span>-alpine3<span class="hljs-number">.11</span>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 国内仓库拉取镜像</span><br>docker <span class="hljs-built_in">run</span> -<span class="hljs-keyword">it</span> <span class="hljs-comment">--name redis01 -d -p 6379:6379 redis  # 映射到6379端口启动redis容器</span><br>docker exec -<span class="hljs-keyword">it</span> redis01 /bin/sh  <span class="hljs-comment"># 进入redis容器</span><br>redis-cli <span class="hljs-comment"># 进入redis自带的交互工具</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">name</span> zhangsan  <span class="hljs-comment"># 存储数据</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">get</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">name</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 获取数据</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-Redis常用的五种数据结构"><a href="#3-Redis常用的五种数据结构" class="headerlink" title="3. Redis常用的五种数据结构"></a>3. Redis常用的五种数据结构</h3><ol><li>key-string     一个key对应一个值</li><li>key-hash       一个key对应一个map<key-value></li><li>key-list       一个key对应一个列表</li><li>key-set      一个key对应一个无序不重复集合</li><li>key-zset     一个key对应一个有序不重复集合</li><li>HyperLogLog   计算近似值</li><li>GEO   存储地理位置</li><li>BIT  存储一个Bit</li></ol><h3 id="4-Redis五种常用的数据结构图"><a href="#4-Redis五种常用的数据结构图" class="headerlink" title="4. Redis五种常用的数据结构图"></a>4. Redis五种常用的数据结构图</h3><p><img src="https://p1-tt.byteimg.com/origin/pgc-image/9ed4d6547d954c5c9ce395a37e188abe.png" alt="1601019295378-ff53f32e-6e87-4370-9d0a-820170b902aa.png"></p><h2 id="String（字符串）"><a href="#String（字符串）" class="headerlink" title="String（字符串）"></a>String（字符串）</h2><figure class="highlight vala"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs vala"><span class="hljs-meta"># 添加值</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> key value<br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 获取值</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">get</span> key<br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 批量添加值</span><br>mset key1 value1 key2 value2<br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 批量获取值</span><br>mget key1 key2<br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 值自增(1)</span><br>incr key<br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 值自减(1)</span><br>decr key<br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 自增自减指定数量</span><br>incrby key <span class="hljs-number">5</span><br>decrby key <span class="hljs-number">5</span><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 设定指定值的生存时间(建议每次添加数据时都指定生存时间)</span><br>setex key <span class="hljs-number">5</span>(second) value<br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 设置值,如果当前key不存在的话  若存在则无任何操作</span><br>setnx key value<br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 在key对应的value后追加内容</span><br>append key value<br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 查看value的长度</span><br>strlen key<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Hash（哈希）"><a href="#Hash（哈希）" class="headerlink" title="Hash（哈希）"></a>Hash（哈希）</h2><p>Map集合 key-<key-value>集合</p><p>存储变更的数据  user  name age ,用户信息的保存  经常变动的信息</p><figure class="highlight vala"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs vala"><span class="hljs-meta"># 存数据</span><br><span class="hljs-meta"># hset key field value</span><br>hset person name zhangsan<br>hset person age <span class="hljs-number">18</span><br>hmset person sex man birth <span class="hljs-number">2020</span><span class="hljs-number">-02</span><span class="hljs-number">-03</span>  ## 批量存储数据<br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 取数据</span><br>hget person age  &gt;&gt;&gt; <span class="hljs-number">18</span><br>  <br><span class="hljs-meta"># 自增(指定自增值)</span><br>hincrby person age <span class="hljs-number">2</span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 设置值,如果key-field不存在的话   若存在则无操作</span><br>hsetnx key fidle value  <br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 检查field是否存在</span><br>hexists key field <br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 删除key对应的field</span><br>hdel key field<br><span class="hljs-meta"># 获取当前hash结构中所有的field和value</span><br>hgetall key<br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 获取当前hash结构中所有的field</span><br>hkeys key<br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 获取当前hash结构中所有的value</span><br>hvals key<br><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 获取当前hash结构中有多少个field</span><br>hlen key<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="List（列表）"><a href="#List（列表）" class="headerlink" title="List（列表）"></a>List（列表）</h2><blockquote><p>List实际上是一个链表，before node after left right都可以插入值</p><p>如果key不存在，则创建新的链表</p><p>如果key存在，新增内容</p><p>如果移除了所有的值，则成为空链表，也代表不存在</p><p>在两边插入或者改动值，效率最高，中间元素，相对来说，效率低一些</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight tcl"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs tcl"><span class="hljs-comment">#  从左侧插入数据</span><br>lpush key value [...value]<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 从右侧插入数据</span><br>rpush key value [...value]<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 修改指定索引的数据</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">lset</span> key index value <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 将一个值插入到已存在的列表的头部或者尾部-------&gt;若key不存在,不进行操作,若key存在,但不是list结构,不进行操作</span><br>lpushx key value  <br>rpushx key value <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 移出并获取列表的第一个 和 最后一个元素</span><br>lpop key<br>rpop key<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 获取指定范围内的数据</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">lrange</span> key start stop  <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看list中所有的数据</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">lrange</span> mylist <span class="hljs-number">0</span> <span class="hljs-number">-1</span> <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 获取指定位置的数据</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">lindex</span> key index<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Set（集合）"><a href="#Set（集合）" class="headerlink" title="Set（集合）"></a>Set（集合）</h2><p>无序集合，不能重复</p><figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br><span class="line">96</span><br><span class="line">97</span><br><span class="line">98</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs clean"><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; sadd myset <span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh01&quot;</span>  ## set添加元素<br>(integer) <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; sadd myset <span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh02&quot;</span><br>(integer) <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; sadd myset <span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh03&quot;</span><br>(integer) <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; smembers myset  ## 查看指定set的值<br><span class="hljs-number">1</span>) <span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh02&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">2</span>) <span class="hljs-string">&quot;hello&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">3</span>) <span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh01&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">4</span>) <span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">5</span>) <span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh03&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; sismember myset hello   ## 判断某一个元素是否再set中<br>(integer) <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; sismember myset world<br>(integer) <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt;<br><br><br>##################################################<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; scard myset   ## 获取set元素个数<br>(integer) <span class="hljs-number">5</span><br><br><br>####################################################<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; srem myset wwh  ## 移除元素<br>(integer) <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><br>####################################################<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; srandmember myset   ### 随机获取元素<br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;hello&quot;</span> <br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt;<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; srandmember myset<br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh02&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; srandmember myset<br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh01&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt;<br><br>######################################################<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; spop myset    ## 随机删除元素<br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh03&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; spop myset<br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh02&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt;<br><br>####################################################<br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; smembers myset<br><span class="hljs-number">1</span>) <span class="hljs-string">&quot;hello&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">2</span>) <span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh01&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; sadd myset2 wwh02<br>(integer) <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; smembers myset2<br><span class="hljs-number">1</span>) <span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh02&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; smove myset myset2 wwh01   ## Set之间移动元素<br>(integer) <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; smembers myset<br><span class="hljs-number">1</span>) <span class="hljs-string">&quot;hello&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">127.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">6379</span>&gt; smembers myset2<br><span class="hljs-number">1</span>) <span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh02&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">2</span>) <span class="hljs-string">&quot;wwh01&quot;</span><br><br>#########################################